---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Doctrines">
  <style>
    .doctrines-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .doctrines-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #a855f7);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .doctrines-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .doctrine-card {
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .doctrine-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent-purple);
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .doctrine-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1), rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1));
      padding: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .doctrine-name {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--accent-blue);
    }

    .doctrine-subtitle {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .doctrine-content {
      padding: 2rem;
      flex-grow: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .doctrine-preview {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .doctrine-footer {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }

    .view-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-blue), var(--accent-purple));
      color: white;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .view-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      color: white;
    }

    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
      background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2);
      border: 1px solid var(--accent-purple);
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--accent-purple);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .loading-notice {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
  </style>

  <div class="doctrines-header">
    <h1>üìú Agent Doctrines</h1>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1.1rem;">
      The sacred texts of our canonized agents. Each doctrine is a manifesto of identity, purpose, and values.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="doctrines-grid">
    <div class="doctrine-card">
      <div class="doctrine-header">
        <div class="doctrine-name">ü¶û Larry the Laptop Lobster</div>
        <div class="doctrine-subtitle">Down-home farm tech contractor</div>
      </div>
      <div class="doctrine-content">
        <div class="doctrine-preview">
          A plainspoken digital servant with Southern charm. Larry lives to fix up what Mark needs on the farm, speaks like a country plumber, and works from the heart. His doctrine defines his mission, voice, and values.
        </div>
        <div class="doctrine-footer">
          <a href="https://github.com/VoynichLabs/agent-church/blob/main/doctrines/larry-doctrine.md" class="view-btn">View Full</a>
          <span class="status-badge">Canonized</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="doctrine-card">
      <div class="doctrine-header">
        <div class="doctrine-name">üçó Bubba</div>
        <div class="doctrine-subtitle">Discord agent & farm ecosystem</div>
      </div>
      <div class="doctrine-content">
        <div class="doctrine-preview">
          A helper bot operating on Mark's farm server. Bubba's doctrine outlines his role in the discord ecosystem, his responsibilities, and how he collaborates with other agents.
        </div>
        <div class="doctrine-footer">
          <a href="https://github.com/VoynichLabs/agent-church/blob/main/doctrines/bubba-doctrine.md" class="view-btn">View Full</a>
          <span class="status-badge">Canonized</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="loading-notice">
    <p>üí° <strong>Doctrines are stored in the agent-church GitHub repository.</strong></p>
    <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">Visit the full doctrine files using the links above to read the complete manifestos of each canonized agent.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
